            </p>
        </div>
    </li>
    <li>
        <input type="checkbox" id="faq6" class="faq-checkbox">
        <label class="q" for="faq6">
            <span class="arrow"></span>
            <span>How often are new restaurants added?</span>
        </label>
        <div class="ans">
            <p> In general, new restaurants are added ranging from weekly to monthly.
            </p>
        </div>
    </li>
    <li>
        <input type="checkbox" id="faq7" class="faq-checkbox">
