        </label>
        <div class="ans">
            <p>Yes, you can filter restaurants based on whether they offer takeout or delivery services.
            </p>
        </div>
    </li>
    <li>
        <input type="checkbox" id="faq8" class="faq-checkbox">
        <label class="q" for="faq8">
            <span class="arrow"></span>
